ate` to a `WallTime`.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/DateTime.html#Std.Time.PlainDate.toWallTime","kind":"def","line":64,"name":"Std.Time.PlainDate.toWallTime","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/68218e876d2a38b1985b8590fff244a83c321783/src/Std/Time/DateTime.lean#L64-L69"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/DateTime.html#Std.Time.WallTime.ofTimestamp\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">WallTime</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofTimestamp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ts</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/DateTime/Timestamp.html#Std.Time.Timestamp\">Timestamp</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">offset</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Offset.html#Std.Time.TimeZone.Offset\">TimeZone.Offset</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Std/Time/DateTime/WallTime.html#Std.Time.WallTime\">WallTime</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Creates a `WallTime` from a `Timestamp` given a timezone `offset`. The result is the local\ncivil time: `wall = UTC + offset`.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/DateTime.html#Std.Time.WallTime.ofTimestamp","kind":"def","line":52,"name":"Std.Time.WallTime.ofTimestamp","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/68218e876d2a38b1985b8590fff244a83c321783/src/Std/Time/DateTime.lean#L52-L58"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/DateTime.html#Std.Time.WallTime.toTimestamp\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">WallTime</span>.<span class=\"name\">toTimestamp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">wt</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/DateTime/WallTime.html#Std.Time.WallTime\">WallTime</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">offset</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Offset.html#Std.Time.TimeZone.Offset\">TimeZone.Offset</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Std/Time/DateTime/Timestamp.html#Std.Time.Timestamp\">Timestamp</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Converts a `WallTime` to a `Timestamp` given a timezone `offset`. The `WallTime` is treated as\ncivil time at the given offset: `UTC = wall − offset`.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/DateTime.html#Std.Time.WallTime.toTimestamp","kind":"def","line":44,"name":"Std.Time.WallTime.toTimestamp","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/68218e876d2a38b1985b8590fff244a83c321783/src/Std/Time/DateTime.lean#L44-L50"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/DateTime.html#Std.Time.Timestamp.ofWallTime\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">Timestamp</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofWallTime</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">wt</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/DateTime/WallTime.html#Std.Time.WallTime\">WallTime</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">offset</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Offset.html#Std.Time.TimeZone.Offset\">TimeZone.Offset</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Std/Time/DateTime/Timestamp.html#Std.Time.Timestamp\">Timestamp</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Creates a `Timestamp` from a `WallTime` and a timezone `offset`. Assumes the `WallTime` represents\ncivil time at the given offset: `UTC = wall − offset`.\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/DateTime.html#Std.Time.Timestamp.ofWallTime","kind":"def","line":32,"name":"Std.Time.Timestamp.ofWallTime","sourceL